get-eventlog system -Newest 5 (give new 5 event log from system)
get-command what command available to run on your computer
--------
Alias
--------
dir is alias for Get-ChildItem (gets the files and folders in a file system drive)
e.g. dir 'C:\Program Files\' -Recurse
Get-Alias -Definition Get-ChildItem

help show-command (This is very handy gives graphical interface)

Get-PSProvider (Gets information about the specified windows powershell provider)

get-psdrive (gets the drive on the machine)

$env:windir or dir $env:windir\system32\*.msc
